              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Automating without a clear strategy. Automation amplifies whatever you feed it — poorly structured campaigns reach more people faster at scale. Build the strategy first, then automate the execution.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Does marketing automation replace marketers?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
